script = ExtResource("1_qd8f6")
release_version = "v1.3.2 (CM37E)"
notes = "[TITLE]Facilities
Increased the size of the grid in the Solicitor's maze from 13x75 to 15x90
  The maze was shrunk slightly to compensate.
The skulls in the Solicitor's maze were made slower too
The Golden Goose and Solicitor now both have a proper level offset.
The Golden Goose can finally no longer crush buttons!
[TITLE]Items
Blue Square Boots: 1.2x Defense -> 1.25x Defense
Hi Top Sneakers: 1.2x Evasiveness -> 1.25x Evasiveness
Swapped the functionality of Fancy Shoes and Sneakers (Fancy Shoes is now Throw and Sneakers is now Lure)
Retextured Fancy Shoes to be its red version instead of its purple version
[TITLE]Proxy Effects
Backtalker: 0.7x Damage -> 0.66x Damage
Banker: +8% Damage Every Round -> +10% Damage Every Round
Diverse Portfolio: 0.7x Damage -> 0.75x Damage
Toxic: Nerfed the damage that Poison/Aftershock can do by about 40%/60% Respectively.
[TITLE]Other
Partner Toons will no longer trigger the Traffic Manager or Bookkeeper's punishments.
  Adjusted a niche interaction with Alien Glasses because of this change."
metadata/_custom_type_script = "uid://d1j0hh6tsgy0r"
